Usage: bam-box --config <config>.json [OPTION]...
QNX8.0 based CD player

  -h, --help                     Output this menu and exit.
  -c, --config       <cfg>       Configuration of bam-box.
  -l, --log-level    <level>     Log level must be one of (ERR, WARN, STAT, INFO, DBG).
  -f, --log-file     <file>      Logging file. If it already exists it will
                                 be appended to the existing log.
  -q, --quiet                    Won't log anything to the console and only the log file
                                 if provided.